## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **elagolix Orilissa 2018** = first FDA GnRH antagonist endometriosis pain. ATP-competitive 7TM 의 small-molecule allosteric paradigm shift. 1990 GnRH agonist (leuprolide) 의 flare + hypoestrogenic 부작용 회피. quantum-VQE 의 7TM allosteric pocket fit.
2. **relugolix-E2-NET Myfembree 2021** = first FDA GnRH antag + estradiol + norethindrone combo endometriosis pain. add-back therapy formulation 으로 hypoestrogenic 부작용 + 골밀도 감소 회피. uterine fibroid (2020) → endometriosis (2022) 적응증 확장. quantum-VQE 의 combination drug binding modeling.
3. **linzagolix Yselty 2022 EU** = next GnRH antagonist — partial dose-dependent E2 suppression + estradiol-add-back-free option. EU + UK + research. US 2024+ pending.
4. **dienogest Visanne 2010 EU/JP / 2017+ KR** = selective PR — 만성 endometriosis pain selective progestin. medroxyprogesterone vs norethindrone vs LNG-IUS 의 receptor-selective 진화. K-pharma framework 에서 1차 progestin 으로 자리잡음.
5. **GnRH agonist (leuprolide + goserelin + triptorelin + nafarelin) 1989-1990** = historical. flare + hypoestrogenic side effect (vasomotor + 골밀도 + cognitive) 가 6 month limit 강제. add-back therapy (norethindrone) 후 쓰임 일부 연장.
6. **danazol 1971** = androgen/anti-gonadotropin. acne + hirsutism + voice change + weight gain 부작용으로 historical. 현재 거의 안 씀.
7. **aromatase inhibitor (letrozole + anastrozole) off-label** = local E2 synthesis 차단 — endometriotic lesion 자체 aromatase 발현 의 합리성. refractory + post-menopausal endometriosis 에 off-label. RCT 한정.
8. **quinagolide research Phase 2** = D2 dopamine agonist. angiogenesis (VEGF) suppression 메커니즘. cross-prolactinoma_specific (Norprolac 적응증). first-in-class endometriosis angiogenesis 표적.
9. **LNG-IUS (Mirena/Liletta) + dienogest** = local progestin delivery. systemic progestin 부작용 회피. adenomyosis 적응증 KR/EU 확대.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, endometriosis 임상 의미 한정. K-pharma 임상 framework + 식약처 산정특례 V248 등 cross-link 만 가능.

